messages.messageBody:
9 New Members - 99 New Messages


Always Learning list, just a minute ago.

I thought that looked cool, 9 and 99.
Not very important.

We've had lots of snow here. It snowed again last night. Sometimes
there's a moment or something really interesting or beautiful, but
photos don't really do it justice. By the time I post this, the 9
and 99 will be gone, if not by my posting, by someone else's posting
or joining the list.

Those fleeting moments can be shared with our kids, too. If they
say, "Mom, come look!" go and look. Don't wait. Some things can't
wait.

Sandra
